item.title: Prayer bpn10183 in Māori
item.description: *KIA KOTAHI TE TĀKINA IA RUA TEKAU MĀ WHĀ HĀORA *Ko ia e hiahia ana ki te taki i tēnei karakia, tukua ia kia tū, ka tahuri ki Te Atua, ā, i a ia e tū ana, tukua ia kia titiro whakatematau, whakatemaui, anō nei ia e tatari ana ki te whai tohu a tōna Ariki, te Tohu Atawhai Rawa, te Mākoha. Kātahi ia ka mea: E ko Koe Te Ariki o ngā ingoa katoa me te Kaihanga o ngā rangi!
